project_descr:
The Construction of  Sewage Treatment Plant and Mian Pressure Line in Khan Younis in the Gaza Strip . 
The project aims at protecting the public health and improving the environmental conditions of Khan Younis residents.

outputs.output_descr: The Construction of Khan Younis Sewage "Waste Water" Treatment Plant and Main Pressure line in Khan Younis Governorate in the Gaza Strip aims at protecting the public health and improving the environmental conditions of Khan Younis residents.
